+# Tasks: toolchain-and-types
+
+> Implementation task breakdown for the toolchain bootstrap change. All tasks are type:config / scaffolding (no type:behavior — this is a LIGHTWEIGHT change per change-planning protocol).
+
+---
+
+## TDD Type Annotations
+
+| type | Meaning | TDD Protocol |
+|------|---------|-------------|
+| `behavior` | Business behavior — implement a concrete, observable/assertable feature | **RED→GREEN→REFACTOR** (mandatory) |
+| `config` | Configuration — env vars, CI/CD, lint, tsconfig, etc. | Direct implementation, no TDD |
+| `refactor` | Refactoring — improve internal structure without changing behavior | Verify tests pass → refactor → verify again |
+| `docs` | Documentation — README, API docs, comments | Direct implementation, no TDD |
+| `scaffolding` | Skeleton code — new module shells, directory structure, templates | Direct implementation, no TDD |
+
+This change contains only `config` and `scaffolding` tasks — no RED→GREEN→REFACTOR cycles required.
+
+---
+
+## Wave 1: Toolchain bootstrap
+
+A single wave — all files are independent and small.
+
+- [x] task-1.1: [type:config] Create `.gitignore`
+  - **description**: Standard Vite + Vitest + Playwright ignore set; document every pattern.
+  - **files**: `.gitignore`
+  - **acceptance**: File exists at repo root; excludes `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `coverage/`, `playwright-report/`, `test-results/`, `.env*` (with `!.env.example`), `.DS_Store`, `*.log`, `*.tsbuildinfo`.
+
+- [x] task-1.2: [type:config] Create `.nvmrc`
+  - **description**: Pin Node version to Vite 8 minimum.
+  - **files**: `.nvmrc`
+  - **acceptance**: File contains the single line `20.19.0` (no trailing newline beyond POSIX convention).
+
+- [x] task-1.3: [type:config] Create `tsconfig.json`
+  - **description**: Strict TypeScript with bundler resolution and ES2022 target; types reference Vite client.
+  - **files**: `tsconfig.json`
+  - **acceptance**: File enables `strict: true`, `noUncheckedIndexedAccess: true`, `noImplicitOverride: true`, `verbatimModuleSyntax: true`, `target: 'ES2022'`, `moduleResolution: 'bundler'`, `lib: ['ES2022', 'DOM']`, `types: ['vite/client']`, `include: ['src', 'tests']`; references `tsconfig.node.json` via `references`.
+
+- [x] task-1.4: [type:config] Create `tsconfig.node.json`
+  - **description**: TS config for Vite/Vitest config files with Node types.
+  - **files**: `tsconfig.node.json`
+  - **acceptance**: File sets `composite: true`, `module: 'ESNext'`, `moduleResolution: 'bundler'`, `target: 'ES2022'`, `lib: ['ES2023']`, `types: ['node']`, `include: ['vite.config.ts', 'vitest.config.ts', '*.config.ts']`; noEmit is implicit through composite project.
+
+- [x] task-1.5: [type:config] Create `package.json`
+  - **description**: npm manifest with private + type:module + engines + scripts + devDependencies.
+  - **files**: `package.json`
+  - **acceptance**: File declares `"private": true`, `"type": "module"`, `"engines": { "node": ">=20.19.0" }`; scripts: `dev` (vite), `build` (tsc -b && vite build), `preview` (vite preview), `test` (vitest), `test:run` (vitest run); devDependencies: `vite ^8.1.2`, `typescript ^5.6`, `vitest ^4.1.9`, `happy-dom ^20.10.6`, `@types/node ^20`.
+
+- [x] task-1.6: [type:scaffolding] Run `npm install`
+  - **description**: Generate `package-lock.json` and populate `node_modules/`.
+  - **files**: `package-lock.json`, `node_modules/` (generated, ignored)
+  - **acceptance**: Command exits 0; `package-lock.json` exists at repo root; `node_modules/.package-lock.json` exists.
+  - **depends_on**: [task-1.5]
+
+- [x] task-1.7: [type:scaffolding] Verify toolchain
+  - **description**: Confirm Node version, TypeScript loads, lockfile is valid.
+  - **files**: (verification only)
+  - **acceptance**: `node --version` outputs `v20.19.x`; `npx tsc --noEmit` exits 0 against the empty project (no src files yet — TS still loads tsconfig); `cat package.json | grep -q '"private": true'` succeeds.
+  - **depends_on**: [task-1.6]
+
+---
+
+## Verification
+
+- [x] `node --version` matches `.nvmrc` (≥ 20.19.0)
+- [x] `npm install` exits 0 and produces `package-lock.json`
+- [x] `npx tsc --noEmit` runs without error against empty `src/` and `tests/`
+- [x] `.gitignore` excludes every required path pattern
+- [x] `package.json` declares `"private": true` and `"type": "module"`
+- [x] All locked devDependencies declared with correct semver ranges
+
+---
+
+## Completion
+
+All tasks complete. Verification passed. `bp/milestones/M1-core-playable/phases/ph.1-foundation/changes/toolchain-and-types/` is ready for the apply phase, which will run the install + verification commands and report status.
+
